# Using VScode extension REST Client (install it and click on 'Send Request' that appears above each request, separate requests with '###')

### TOURNAMENT

### Get all tournaments
GET http://localhost:3000/tournaments HTTP/1.1

### Get all tournaments from a specific player
GET http://localhost:3000/tournaments/player/<id> HTTP/1.1

### Get specific tournament
GET http://localhost:3000/tournaments/<id> HTTP/1.1

### Create a new tournament
POST http://localhost:3000/tournaments/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
	"name": "newTournament",
	"maxParticipants": 4,
	"createdBy": "<id>",
	"settings": "{\"map\":\"testing\",\"rounds\":3}"
}

### Update a tournament
PUT http://localhost:3000/tournaments/<id> HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
	"status": "ACTIVE",
	"currentRound": 2,
}
